<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Moose & Me Baking Co.</h1>
    <p>Ad Campaign Proposal: "Made With Heart, Shared With Joy"</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Client Proposal</h2>
    <p>We created this campaign for Moose & Me to increase brand awareness, seasonal sales, and overall visibility through heartfelt and visually connected ads across multiple platforms. Our goal is to share the love and joy that Moose & Me puts into every baked treat with families and gift-givers in the community.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Campaign Elements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Slogan:</strong> "Made With Heart, Shared With Joy"</li>
      <li><strong>Colors:</strong> Warm pastels, cream, and brown tones</li>
      <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Script-style headers and clean body text</li>
      <li><strong>Tone:</strong> Nostalgic, community-focused, heartfelt</li>
      <li><strong>Visuals:</strong> Real product photography, happy customer moments</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Target Market</h2>
    <p><strong>Primary:</strong> Women 25–55, local moms, event organizers, and gift-givers<br />
       <strong>Secondary:</strong> Young adults 18–30, social media users, holiday shoppers</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Media Strategy</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Instagram & Facebook Ads</li>
      <li>In-store Posters and Flyers</li>
      <li>Local Print Publications</li>
  
    </ul>
  </section>

