  <section>
    <h2>Why This Campaign Works</h2>
    <p>This campaign connects all advertising with a shared emotional message and a cozy, consistent visual identity. Each ad targets customers where they shop, scroll, or stop, ensuring Moose & Me stays top-of-mind during every season and celebration.</p>
